From [~skleinei]:

{quote}
It seems that our Extractors (as well as built-in Extractors such as CommentExtractor) do not get called when a page is created. Also, IndexQueueFlushCompleteEvent is never thrown (at least in our tests). Is this on purpose or will this change in the next beta?

