When a page has restrictions and a user tries to move the page into a different parent page, Confluence will throw the following error message: !screenshot004 (1).jpg!

However, the error message will not be clearly visible to the user when there are many pages (or it has a huge hierarchy). Therefore, when the user tries to move it, the page seems to be successfully moved (but it's actually not, because the error message is located at the top of the page).

